column2: SELECT top #   m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,    stack.class AS class, stack.subClass  AS subClass,    stack.ra AS ra_spec,  stack.dec AS dec_spec   stack.z AS z_spec,  stack.zWarning	 AS zWarning	  FROM MyDB.millionandhalftrainsam_radec AS m     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS stack ON n.objid=stack.objID
